<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT1.8">
<l>nāṭu nakarun tirintu ceṉṟu naṉṉeṟi nāṭi nayantavarai</l>
<l>mūṭi mutupiṇat tiṭṭa māṭē muṉṉiya pēykkaṇañ cūḻac cūḻak</l>
<l>kāṭuṅ kaṭalu malaiyu maṇṇum viṇṇuñ cuḻala vaṉalkaiyēnti</l>
<l>yāṭu maravap puyaṅka ṉeṅka ḷappa ṉiṭamtiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of our father who is adorned with snakes, who dances,</l>
<l>hand held up with fire, while cremation ground, sea, mountain, earth and sky spin around,</l>
<l>while groups of demonesses are all around that have approached the side where old corpses were placed,</l>
<l>shrouding those who had been full of longing, roaming, going to land and city, seeking the good path,</l>
	<l>is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
